      "name": "FDA generic pump hemolysis benchmark comparison — MRL 5 assessment",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted hemolysis index against experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark dataset. Prediction interval from Monte Carlo UQ overlaps experimental scatter but systematic over-prediction observed at high-speed operating points. Validation metric: normalised hemolysis index GCI < 8% on finest mesh; however model-form error dominates uncertainty budget. Achieved validation level insufficient for MRL 5 absolute hemolysis claims.",
      "validationMetric": "Normalised hemolysis index (NIH)",
      "comparisonOutcome": "Insufficient — systematic bias exceeds acceptance band at 3 of 5 operating conditions"
    },
    {
